<s> Giant Group Ltd. said it terminated negotiations for the purchase of Aspen Airways , a Denver-based regional carrier that operates the United Express connector service under contract to UAL Corp. 's United Airlines . </s>
<s> Giant , a Beverly Hills , Calif. , collection of companies that is controlled by Hollywood producer Burt Sugarman , did n't give a reason for halting its plan to acquire the airline , and Aspen officials could n't be reached for comment . </s>
<s> Giant agreed last month to purchase the carrier . </s>
<s> Giant has n't ever disclosed the proposed price , although Avmark Inc. , an Arlington , Va.-based aircraft consulting concern , has valued Aspen 's fleet at about $ 46 million . </s>
<s> The airline would have become the latest in a peculiar blend of Giant companies , which are involved in making cement , recycling newsprint and operating fast-food restaurants . </s>
